'''''Nel sole''''' is a [[List of Italian films of 1967|1967]] [[Cinema of Italy|Italian]] [[musicarello]] film directed by [[Aldo Grimaldi]]. The title is a reference to the [[Albano Carrisi|Al Bano]]'s [[nel sole|hit song with the same name]].<ref name="60-69 m-z">{{cite book|last=Roberto Poppi, Mario Pecorari|title=Dizionario del cinema italiano. I film|publisher=Gremese Editore, 2007|isbn=8884405033}}</ref><ref name=stracult>{{cite book|last=Marco Giusti|title=Dizionario dei film italiani stracult|year=1999|publisher=Sperling & Kupfer|isbn=8820029197}}</ref>

